


tree

├── client             <--- gia to spiti 
│   └── ifup_linux     <--  config gia ton client
├── okeanos            <--  okeanos
│   ├── ifup_linux     <--  config gia okeanos
│   ├── settings
│   └── user           <-- katalogos gia auto insert user
│       ├── cs131094@uniwa.gr.USER   <-- entoli gia na valeis user
│       ├── cs171009@uniwa.gr.USER
│       └── rootapostolos@swarmlab.io.USER
├── run-client.sh      <-- start client sto spiti
├── run.yml            <-- yml gia okeanos
├── run.yml.sh         <-- start service on okeanos
└── stop-all.sh        



1.  install wireguard on Host (Spiti kai okeanos)

	sudo apt update && sudo apt install wireguard

	Now sudo modprobe wireguard doesn't complain, and lsmod | grep wireguard shows:

	wireguard             212992  0
	ip6_udp_tunnel         16384  1 wireguard
	udp_tunnel             16384  1 wireguard


2. create kleidia (spiti kai okeanos)
  	wg genkey | tee privatekey | wg pubkey > publickey 

OKENAOS
-------
1. edit okeanos if_up 
	   wg set swarmlab0 listen-port 51820 private-key /settings/connect/privatekey    
							  ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^      edo vazeis to private to path messa sto docker des sto yml edo - [FullPath]/okeanos:/settings/connect
	   iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -o eth0 -j MASQUERADE
					    ^^^^^                 prosexeis edo na dichni to allo interface messa sto docker - ektos tou swarmlab0
2. edit run.yml sto simio - [FullPath]/okeanos:/settings/connect

3. run 
   ./ run.yml.sh 

spiti
----
1. edit if_up
   stin grammi 3   vazeis to private to diko sou - apo to spiti
   stin grammi 8   vazeis to public tou okeanos
   stin grammi 11  vazeis tin official ip tou server ston okeanos kai tin antistichi port pou evales na pexi to dockera - diladi edo  38521:51820/udp to 38521 sto paradeigma
   stin grammi 24  vazeis tin ip pou tha sou dossi o server - vlepe  "pos vazo user"

2. edit run-client.sh
   stin grammi  9 vazeis to path opou vriskonte ta files tou client

3. run 
   ./run-client.sh


4. mpenis mesa sto docker
   cd sto    /settingsclient
   run      sh ./ifup_linux

pos vaso user
------------


efoson trechei mpenis sto docker    me     docker exec -it image-id /bin/bash

kai trecheis to parakato

wg set swarmlab0 peer M1dcCRZM650kwwGvamT4T/7lKWCJgNnrk73gSZ4FiBI= allowed-ips 10.1.2.68 
       ^^^^^^^^        ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^                ^^^^^^^
       interface         public tou user pou tha valeis                          IP pou tha doseis




